== Basics ==

* Configuration
* command-line options
* help (cf. SPECS)

== Additional Features ==

* scheduled tasks
* RegEx support
** list-filtering
** replacing
* list nanoformats (e.g. projects, contexts)
* simple logger (non-task items in separate file)
* alternative stores
** TiddlyWeb
** multi-store (simultaneously saving to two or more stores)
* GUI

== Misc. ==

* code analysis (PyLint, PyChecker, PyFlakes)
* license (BSD?)
* i18n: move strings to separate object
